wiki.summary: This tracks title, “TELEKINESIS”, is a reference to the supposed ability of moving objects via one’s mind. It is often fictionally portrayed in Superhero films and comics, which Travis has a liking to, even dressing as his favorites on multiple occasions including Batman and Iron-Man. It was formerly Kanye West’s, and was tentatively titled “Future Sounds”, containing a feature from none other than Travis himself — recorded during sessions for West’s Donda. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: This tracks title, “TELEKINESIS”, is a reference to the supposed ability of moving objects via one’s mind. It is often fictionally portrayed in Superhero films and comics, which Travis has a liking to, even dressing as his favorites on multiple occasions including Batman and Iron-Man. It was formerly Kanye West’s, and was tentatively titled “Future Sounds”, containing a feature from none other than Travis himself — recorded during sessions for West’s Donda. However it would be heavily re-worked to feature Future & SZA, where they create a soundscape that is magical, like telekinesis. Read more on Last.fm.
